{"tid":2395794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK Lisa曬甜辣蕾絲內衣舞台Look，超像這個卡通人物啊XD","createTime":"2021-02-05T06:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T05:51:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1dee9f84cde8184e89ca7432ce86c4e0a17c65c7","tid":2395794,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_adbeb4a9c0b91d171d7a71675cc22666/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-04/133492-895995.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_adbeb4a9c0b91d171d7a71675cc22666%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-04%2F133492-895995.png&h=92b3c04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK成員Lisa更新了一張新照，讓所有粉絲看了都直呼：「這也太辣了吧」。<br />\n<br />\nLisa在個人IG裡分享了一張穿著甜美性感風蕾絲內衣的照片，其實是她在之前的BLACKPINK線上演唱會上的造型。 Lisa將黑色的長髮扎成雙馬尾，上半身穿的是黑色胸衣，外面加了一件粉色羽毛馬甲，下半身則是黑色短裙和粉色漁網襪，性感又俏皮。 白皙的皮膚和纖瘦的身材，看得女生們都驚呼身材太棒了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lalalalisa_m/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flalalalisa_m%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=5c92540b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lalalalisa_m/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n有粉絲看到Lisa的這個造型後聯想到了《美少女戰士》裡的月野兔（水手月亮），都是大長腿和雙馬尾，Lisa的嬌俏甜辣風格，大家愛了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sailor_movie?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1354942355229478913%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F133492\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsailor_movie%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1354942355229478913%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.koreastardaily.com%252Ftc%252Fnews%252F133492&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=d8f07d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">